{"tid":1166881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【西鐵避雨狗】漁護署尋獲狗主　對方簽紙棄養","createTime":"2019-05-22T17:05:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T08:52:18.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"18ec24e5bdab35244a8261a76350b7a4d2a148a7","tid":1166881,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T17:05:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2828354/org/2e996c8fcc43f6b7befc0101934312cb.jpg/1ehpJYr0fHPIVlALIkzJeih7uBkVSFSR_J7ISvyeyEo?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2828354%2Forg%2F2e996c8fcc43f6b7befc0101934312cb.jpg%2F1ehpJYr0fHPIVlALIkzJeih7uBkVSFSR_J7ISvyeyEo%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=f43dabc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《香港01》早前報道，有一隻狗隻於周一（21日）晚上大雨下走入西鐵綫列車內，及後被港鐵職員帶走。漁農自然護理署今晚（22日）回覆《香港01》查詢時指，已尋獲狗主，但對方已簽紙棄養，狗隻暫時交由署方作進一步的檢查。<br />\n<br />\n漁護署發言人證實，署方人員已經成功聯絡狗隻蓄養人，但對方表明並簽紙棄養。有關狗隻目前在署方轄下的動物管理中心暫住，經獸醫初步檢查後，有關狗隻沒有表面傷痕，獸醫將為狗隻作進一步的檢查。<br />\n<br />\n關注動物權益的民主黨立法會議員鄺俊宇表示，會去信漁護署了解狗隻情況。他指該隻狗性格溫馴，署方應將狗隻交予動物福利機構安排領養。<br />\n<br />\n香港動物報創辦人梁美寶表示，愛護動物協會或獲漁護署認可動物機構，才有機會領取有關狗隻。她又稱，按現時機制，狗隻原主人如不願轉名或要求人道毀滅，該狗隻亦不能倖免，故漁護署亦應檢討人道毀滅程序，「畀條生路佢行」。"},{"pid":"ca5096f40f53f67438f426f587d40ad294d9c9a6","tid":1166881,"uid":16123,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T17:09:16.000Z","msg":"棄養死全家"},{"pid":"81f5eac4410a43ea9d6dfb4269b25ac897b364c8","tid":1166881,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T17:30:36.000Z","msg":"呵呵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feda4c13fd80a882d101d858c916792246fe7bed","tid":1166881,"uid":65395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T22:29:49.000Z","msg":"開名"},{"pid":"b35df694dc5c3184cac355753e8487d896d57a95","tid":1166881,"uid":35790,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T23:12:23.000Z","msg":"已尋獲狗主，但對方已簽紙棄養，狗隻暫時交由署方作進一步的檢查。<br />\n<br />\n狗主最pk<br />\n攞明放隻狗去死(人道毀滅)"},{"pid":"06b88c0b0ec0ee4d9ad6dfca7a00c689e03df09e","tid":1166881,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T23:24:06.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以領養呀<br />\n佢真係好乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26d28ba102d480f3e96a229f734ba4012657ac8f","tid":1166881,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06b88c0b0ec0ee4d9ad6dfca7a00c689e03df09e","tid":1166881,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T23:24:06.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以領養呀<br />\n佢真係好乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T23:28:58.000Z","msg":"係就快手<br />\n因為漁農署仲手快"},{"pid":"5fc16b89bbe7169f31dab8aa094fd85569d9dc4c","tid":1166881,"uid":64009,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"06b88c0b0ec0ee4d9ad6dfca7a00c689e03df09e","tid":1166881,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T23:24:06.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以領養呀<br />\n佢真係好乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T00:40:25.000Z","msg":"你唔養?"},{"pid":"30d725dec79d932bfad1b06ac6aed379e90f61cd","tid":1166881,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T00:50:10.000Z","msg":"仆街主人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"226789dbf92de5784fceb694ab9571f55b0a011e","tid":1166881,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T00:53:16.000Z","msg":"好想去領養佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ed98cc379c26346e9564a2b7d6caaa8b07c23b","tid":1166881,"uid":47462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T00:57:44.000Z","msg":"將個狗主人道毀滅ok?"},{"pid":"a22c42321649c97f5e7243728e2164d62503e3f1","tid":1166881,"uid":88763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s